# English only

**All files in this repository must be written in English.**

This applies to:

- Source code, tests, and configuration
- Comments and JSDoc/TSDoc
- Documentation (`README.md`, `AGENTS.md`, `CONTRIBUTING.md`, changelogs)
- Cursor rules (`.cursor/rules/*.mdc`)
- Commit messages and PR descriptions (when the agent writes them)
- User-facing error messages and log prefixes in application code
- Variable names, function names, and API surface strings

Do **not** create or edit project files in Polish or any other language, even if the user communicates in another language.

Exception: replying to the user in chat may use their preferred language; repository artifacts remain English.
